item.title: Gunung Api Purba Nglanggeran
item.description: Just learning English, It was monday, 29 december when I was in Yogya. I went to yogya to attend my relative’s wedding party in 28. My train seted out on 29 in the night. I was sick and tired to stay in my grandma’s house. Actually, I have made the itinerary if I visit Yogya again. But the plan is just a plan. I don’t know, its not because I’m scared of travelling alone but i’m too lazy to go anywhere so whenever I go to yogya I always spent my time on my grandma’s house.

item.title: Beyond Music is Haram
